zandalee is a 1991 american erotic thriller/romantic tragedy which was shot entirely in new orleans , released in 1991 , starring nicolas cage , judge reinhold , erika anderson , marisa tomei , joe pantoliano , viveca lindfors , aaron neville , and steve buscemi .   the film was directed by sam pillsbury .   although the film played theatrically in some countries , it was released straight to video in the united states .   the film steals liberally from émile zola 's novel and play thérèse raquin .